  <h2>DIY In-House Plans <em>(the real #1)</em> <span class="pill pill-wine">HIGHEST THREAT</span></h2>
  <div class="card">
    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem">
