      <div class="lbl">Landmines to lay</div>
      <p style="margin:0">"Who carries the liability when your state asks about your unlicensed plan?" · "How much are you discounting vs. a structured plan — have you modeled the leakage?" · "Who runs renewals and compliance filings when the front desk is slammed?"</p>
